('FR (France)', 'Direction de l''Évaluation, de la Prospective et de la Performance - Directorate of Evaluation, Forecasting, and Performance - Panel 2007 (entrants en sixième)', 'DEPP 2007', 'The French DEPP Panel 2007 contains longitudinal and administrative data following approximately 35,000 students from sixth grade into adulthood. It includes detailed information on students'' and families'' socio-demographic characteristics, their cultural and material environments, and the development of students’ cognitive skills over time. Data is available upon request.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2007, 2017, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 35000, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.education.gouv.fr/les-panels-d-eleves-de-la-depp-source-essentielle-pour-connaitre-et-evaluer-le-systeme-educatif-4871', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes'),
('FR (France)', 'Direction de l''Évaluation, de la Prospective et de la Performance - Directorate of Evaluation, Forecasting, and Performance - Panel 2011 (entrants CP)', 'DEPP 2011', 'The French DEPP Panel 2011 contains longitudinal and administrative data following 15,200 first graders for 5 years (based on publicly available data). It includes detailed information on students'' and families'' socio-demographic characteristics, their cultural and material environments, and the development of students’ cognitive skills over time. Data is available upon request.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2011, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 15200, 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.education.gouv.fr/les-panels-d-eleves-de-la-depp-source-essentielle-pour-connaitre-et-evaluer-le-systeme-educatif-4871', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, geographical area', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No'),
('FR (France)', 'Étude Longitudinale Française depuis l''Enfance - French Longitudinal Study of Children', 'ELFE', 'ELFE contains data on over 18,000 children tracked from birth into adulthood as part of a national longitudinal study in France. It covers multiple aspects of children''s lives, including education, family dynamics, environmental conditions, and health. Cognitive and developmental assessments are conducted during early childhood education, as well as in first and fourth grades. Data is accessible upon request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2011, 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 18000, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.elfe-france.fr/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, full ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, geographical area', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No'),
('DE (Germany)', 'National Education Panel Study (Nationales Bildungspanel) - Starting Cohort Grade 5 (2010; SC3)', 'NEPS (SC3)', 'This dataset contains data from the Fifth-grade Starting Cohort of the German National Educational Panel Study (NEPS), launched in 2010. It follows approximately 5,000 students from early adolescence into adulthood, focusing on the development of competencies and educational trajectories over time. Data is collected by the Leibniz Institute for Educational Trajectories and is accessible upon request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2010, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 5000, 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Open data', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.neps-data.de/Datenzentrum/Daten-und-Dokumentation/SC3-Klasse-5', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, full ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes'),
