('BE (Flanders)', 'Loopbanen in het Secundair Onderwijs (Trajectories in Secondary Education)', 'LiSO project', 'LiSO is a cohort study following approximately 6,500 Flemish students through secondary education, from seventh to twelfth grade. It assesses their cognitive and non-cognitive skills, as well as collecting information on their background and school experience. Currently, only a select group of researchers can access the data, but it may be possible to access it upon request in the future.', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2013, 2019, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 6500, 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://onderwijs.vlaanderen.be/ and https://data-onderwijs.vlaanderen.be/onderwijsonderzoek/project/421', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes, only presence/absence', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Not clear', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('LU (Luxemburg)', 'Épreuves Standardisées (Standardized tests)', 'ÉpStan', 'EpStan consists of standardized and longitudinal achievement tests administered each fall in Luxembourg''s schools, measuring students'' skills in Luxembourgish, French, German, and mathematics. The tests are given to the entire population of first, third, fifth, seventh, and ninth grade students. Access to raw data is restricted, but the result reports are fully accessible', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pseudo-panel', 'Survey', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2009, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://epstan.lu/fr/informations-generales', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
