('IT (Italy)', 'Anagrafe Nazionale degli Studenti - Open data', 'ANS OPEN', 'The ANS Open Data provides aggregated administrative statistics on student enrollments, transfers, and final outcomes across all school levels (from preschool to upper secondary) in Italy. Data are available by region, school type, and grade, and are accessible without registration via the Ministry of Education’s open data portal. ', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2014, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 500000, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://dati.istruzione.it/opendata/opendata/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No'),
('DE (Germany)', 'Twin Life: Eine längsschnittliche Zwillingsfamilienstudie (cohort 1)', 'TwinLife (C1)', 'Twin Life contains longitudinal data regarding German twin families, focusing on their education and career, behaviour, participation in social and political life and perceived opportunities. Partecipants are followed yearly. Cohort 1 follows children born in 2009/2010. Data are accessible upon request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2014, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 1000, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.twin-life.de', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
