('IT (Italy)', 'Anagrafe Nazionale Studenti microdata', 'ANS Microdata', 'The ANS microdata contain individual-level administrative records on students attending Italian schools from preschool to upper secondary education. The dataset tracks educational careers over time, including enrollments, transitions, and completions. Access is restricted to accredited researchers and institutions upon formal request and subject to approval. ', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2005, 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 5000, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://www.mim.gov.it/-/anagrafe-nazionale-degli-studen-3', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No'),
('NO (Norway)', 'The Behaviour Outlook Norwegian Developmental Study', 'BONDS', 'The Norwegian BONDS data collects information on children''s social competences, behavioural problems, and development from 6 months to 8th grade, including family, childcare, and school factors. It covers national reading and math test results in grades 5 and 8, across five Southeast Norway municipalities. Data access is available upon request to the data owners. ', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2006, 2021, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 1159, 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.nubu.no/barnssosialeutvikling/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes, precise number', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, geographical area', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
