('NO (Norway)', 'National Education Database', 'SSB/NUDB', 'The SSB/NUDB data are Norwegian population data collected by Statistics Norway. They cover the entire student population. Administrative information on students is collected annually, while national tests are administered only in grades 5, 8, and 9, in three subjects: reading, mathematics, and a foreign language. Access to microdata is accessible upon formal request and subject to approval. ', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2007, 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.ssb.no/en/utdanning', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
