('NL (Netherlands)', 'Children of Immigrants Longitudinal Survey in the Netherlands', 'CILSNL', 'CILSNL is a 7-year longitudinal study launched in 2010, following a national sample of 14-year-olds in the Netherlands, including both immigrant-origin students and a native reference group. It tracks educational progress, integration, values, and social participation across all school tracks. Data are accessible to researchers through CILS4EU application procedures.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2010, 2017, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 3600, 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.nwo.nl/en/projects/480-11-013-0', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes'),
('BE (Flanders)', 'Schoolloopbanen in het basisonderwijs', 'SiBO ', 'The SiBO project tracks school careers from the final year of kindergarten (K3) through primary education in the Flemish Community of Belgium. It follows 6,138 students from 196 schools. Assessments include reading, comprehension, spelling, math, and cognitive ability tests. The data include identifiers for administrative linkage, but access to microdata is restricted to data owners.', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2002, 2011, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 6138, 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://onderwijs.vlaanderen.be/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, full ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes'),
('UK (England, Wales, Scotland, Northern Ireland)', 'Families and Schools Together', 'FAST', 'Families and Schools Together (FAST) is a UK-based study evaluating the impact of a parental engagement programme on children attainment, and social and emotional outcomes. It involves 4,221 pupils across 115 schools over 1.5 years. Data access is restricted; microdata are not publicly available without permission.', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2015, 2017, 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 4221, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'https://educationendowmentfoundation.org.uk/projects-and-evaluation/projects/families-and-schools-together-fast', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('UK (England, Wales, Scotland, Northern Ireland)', 'Children’s University', 'CU', 'Children’s University is a 4-year study evaluating a youth social action program for pupils across the UK. The programme aims to improve the aspirations and attainment of pupils aged 5 to 14 by providing learning activities beyond the normal school day. Test includes assessments of reading and mathematics. Data were collected as part of an Education Endowment Foundation initiative. Microdata access is limited and by request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2014, 2016, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'https://educationendowmentfoundation.org.uk/projects-and-evaluation/projects/childrens-university', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('AT (Austria)', 'Wege in die Zukunft (Paths into the Future) - Längsschnittstudie über die Vergesellschaftung junger Menschen in Wien', 'Wege in die Zukunft', 'Wege in die Zukunft is a five-year longitudinal study based in Vienna, Austria, tracking 14–15-year-old students from the final year of lower secondary school. Using a mixed-methods design, it examines how social background, education, and labor market conditions shape life paths. Microdata access is restricted and not publicly available.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2018, 2022, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 2850, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'https://www.soz.univie.ac.at/forschung/wege-in-die-zukunft-institutsprojekt/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Adolescents’ well-being and learning in future society', 'FRAM', 'FRAM is a four-year longitudinal study (2016–2019) in Finland examining the links between academic well-being, achievement, and educational pathways. It follows students from grades 7 and 9 using an accelerated design, collecting school grades in Finnish and mathematics. Data access is available upon request from project managers at Åbo Akademi University.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2016, 2019, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 612, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://research.abo.fi/en/projects/adolescent-students-well-being-and-learning-in-future-society', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Bridging the Gaps', 'GAPS (2017-2021)', 'GAPS (2017–2021) is a longitudinal study in Finland examining the impact of digitalization on youth development across cognitive, emotional, and social domains. It follows three cohorts born in 1997, 2000, and 2005 using innovative methods including fMRI, biomarkers, and smartphone-based experience sampling. Data access is restricted and must be requested from project coordinators.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2013, 2021, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 426, 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://growingmind.fi/bridging-the-gaps/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'INVEST data', 'INVEST', 'INVEST is a national Finnish dataset (2014–2022) combining administrative records from Statistics Finland and the Finnish Institute for Health and Welfare. It includes comprehensive register data to study social, educational, and health outcomes. Microdata access is available upon request and subject to approval by the data providers.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2014, 2022, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Computer-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://investdata.utu.fi/catalog/studies/9a9761da-26dc-45af-a047-3f1cda786db3', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Student engagement, truancy, and cynicism: A longitudinal study from primary school to upper secondary education', NULL, 'This longitudinal Finnish study followed approximately 2000 children from four Finnish municipalities were followed 10 times from kindergarten to the end of lower secondary school, exploring how engagement trajectories relate to truancy and school cynicism. The anonymized dataset is not publicly accessible and requires special permission for use.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2006, 2018, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 1835, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://doi.org/10.1016/j.lindif.2021.101972', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Dynamics between perceived social support and study engagement among primary school students: A three-year longitudinal survey', NULL, 'This three-year longitudinal study (2017–2019) followed 2400 fourth-grade students from 63 comprehensive schools across Finland. Study examines the relationship between perceived social support and study engagement. Data were collected annually in classrooms. Microdata are not publicly available and access is limited.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2017, 2019, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 2400, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11218-022-09734-2', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear');
