('RO (Romania)', 'Training and Development in Education System', 'TRAIDES', 'The Transylvania Adolescent Identity Development Study (TRAIDES) is a longitudinal panel study conducted during the 2013–2014 school year in the North-Western region of Romania. It includes students from grades 8 to 12 across seven schools. Data were collected over three waves. The sample is not nationally representative, and data access is restricted.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2013, 2014, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 1151, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://selfid.eu/traides/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('FR (France)', 'Système de Suivi des Candidats (Candidate Tracking System) ', 'SYSCA', 'SYSCA is an ongoing longitudinal study in France, launched in 2018, following students in grades 6, 8, and 10. It aims to track educational experiences and outcomes over time. The study covers various school contexts, but data access is limited and subject to approval by the responsible research institutions.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Survey', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2018, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a computer belonging to the producer of the data, which is not connected to internet or to another computer (in this case the producer examines all the results outputs)', 'Not available', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('DK (Denmark)', 'Administrative Register Data', NULL, 'Statistics Denmark collects annual administrative data covering the entire student population across all educational levels and subjects. The dataset includes student flows, attainment, and mobility, supporting both official statistics and register-based research. Data access is limited to researchers based in Denmark or to institutions with an established formal collaboration with a Danish partner. A formal request alone is not sufficient to gain access.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 'not clear', 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.dst.dk/da/Statistik/dokumentation/Times/uddannelsesdata', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes'),
('ES (Spain)', 'Education Data at the Catalan Department of Education', 'RALC', 'The Catalan Department of Education maintains administrative education data for the population of Catalonia, collected primarily for policy purposes. RALC provides statistics on student enrollments, grades, and final outcomes across all school levels (from preschool to upper secondary). Data access requires a detailed application, and approved datasets are custom-built and shared under strict conditions.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2013, 'ongoing', 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://educacio.gencat.cat/ca/departament/estadistiques/acces-informacio-estadistica-dades/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Mind the GAP (2013-2016)', 'GAPS (2013-2016)', 'Mind the GAP (2013–2016) is a four-year longitudinal study conducted in the capital area of Finland. It explores gaps between educational practices and the development of adolescents aged 12, 16, and 20 who have grown up with digital technologies. Part of the Academy of Finland’s Human Mind program. Data access is restricted and by request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2013, 2016, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 749, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://growingmind.fi/projects/mind-the-gap/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('ES (Spain)', 'Evaluaciones de diagnóstico - Canary Islands ', 'ACCUEE', 'ACCUEE provides data from diagnostic assessments in 3th, 4th, 6th, 8th and 10th grade in the Canary Islands, covering covering numeracy, literacy and science skills. Since 2016, around 3,500 pupils have been assessed annually. Data are available by region, school type, and grade, and can be accessed openly via the Ministry of Education’s data portal.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pseudo-panel', 'Hybrid', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2016, 'ongoing', 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 3448, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'https://www3.gobiernodecanarias.org/educacion/accuee/nouniversitario/evadiag', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear'),
('PT (Portugal)', 'Portuguese Longitudinal Study on School Engagement', NULL, 'This national longitudinal study follows students from Grade 7 to Grade 12 across Scientific-Humanities and Vocational courses in Portugal. It includes assessments in reading, speaking, comprehension, and mathematics, along with socio-economic background data. No teacher data is included. Microdata are not publicly available and were accessed through private contacts.', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Every other year', 2012, 2018, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://cipd.ulusiada.pt/ ', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No'),
('DE (Germany)', 'Vergleichsarbeiten (Vera)', 'VERA', 'Vergleichsarbeiten (VERA) are nationwide comparative assessments conducted in Germany since 2004 for grades 3 and 8. They test German (e.g., reading, listening, orthography), mathematics, and a first foreign language (English or French). While cross-sectional, data enable pseudo-panel analyses. Microdata access is limited.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pseudo-panel', 'Survey', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2004, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'No access', 'https://www.iqb.hu-berlin.de/vera/', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('SE (Sweden)', 'Gothenburg Educational Longitudinal Database', 'GOLD', 'The Gothenburg Educational Longitudinal Database (GOLD) includes all individuals born between 1972 and 2004 in Sweden. It provides detailed administrative data on primary and upper secondary education, including grades, program choices, and admissions. Data include an identification code that allows linkability to other administrative data. Access is restricted to researchers affiliated with the University of Gothenburg and must remain within the EU/EEA.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Administrative', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 1961, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 9000, 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer without a specific interface', 'https://www.gu.se/pedagogik-specialpedagogik/gold', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, full ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No'),
('FI (Finland)', 'Finnish National Agency for Education''s national central integration service for study rights and achievements', 'KOSKI', 'KOSKI is Finland’s national education database managed by the Finnish National Agency for Education. Since 2018, it has collected annual data on student records, school grades, study rights, and qualifications from pre-primary through vocational education. It integrates with national systems for use by social, educational, and immigration authorities. Microdata access is restricted.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2018, 2025, 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Computer-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://www.oph.fi/fi/palvelumme/koski-palvelu', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear');
