('FR (France)', 'Évaluations repères', 'Évaluations repères', 'Évaluations repères is national benchmark assessment conducted annually in France since 2018 at several grades during primary education to measure the progress of students'' achievements in certain areas of reading and mathematics. Designed to identify student needs early in the school year, they help tailor support throughout the academic year. The data have national coverage, and aggregated results are publicly available via the Ministry of Education’s website, microdata are not available.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2018, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Paper-based', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Full access through request', 'On a computer belonging to the producer of the data, which is not connected to internet or to another computer (in this case the producer examines all the results outputs)', 'https://www.education.gouv.fr/les-evaluations-nationales-exhaustives-307627', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('PT (Portugal)', 'Provas de Aferição do Ensino Básico, Exames Nacionais do Ensino Básico, Exames Nacionais do Ensino Secundário', 'PAEB, ENEB, ENES', 'Portugal’s national assessment system includes PAEB, ENEB, and ENES — exams with available information on student’s classifications since 2012. PAEB are conducted in grades 2, 4, 5 or 6; ENEB in grade 9 (at the end of basic education); and ENES in grades 11 and 12 (at the end of secondary education). These assessments cover a wide range of subjects and apply to the entire student population. Access to microdata is restricted and requires on-site presence at DGEEC, the data owner.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Hybrid', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2012, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a computer belonging to the producer of the data, which is not connected to internet or to another computer (in this case the producer examines all the results outputs)', 'https://www.dge.mec.pt/relatoriosestatisticas-0', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('PT (Portugal)', 'Estatísticas Oficiais de Educação e Formação', 'EEF', 'Estatísticas Oficiais de Educação e Formação (EEF) is part of national assessment covering all levels of education from pre-school to grade 12. Collected since 2008, it includes school grades in literacy, mathematics, and science supported by information related to higher education, namely students characteristics, graduates, enrollments, and faculty. Data access is restricted and subject to formal approval.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2008, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a computer belonging to the producer of the data, which is not connected to internet or to another computer (in this case the producer examines all the results outputs)', 'https://www.dgeec.medu.pt/art/educacao-pre-escolar-basico-e-secundario', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, specific country', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('EL/GR (Greece)', 'MySchool', 'MySchool', 'MySchool is Greece’s national education management system, active since 2014. It provides continuous administrative data on all students, including records on grades, absences, disciplinary actions, and performance. Each student has a unique identifier. Data are updated regularly, but access is restricted and requires formal approval.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2014, 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://myschool.sch.gr', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, specific country', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes'),
('CH (Switzerland)', 'The Zurich Project on the Social Development from Childhood to Adulthood', 'Z-PROSO ', 'The Zurich Project on the Social Development from Childhood to Adulthood (z-proso) is a longitudinal study conducted in the city of Zurich, Switzerland. It has followed over 1,400 children since they entered primary school in 2004, examining behavioral development and educational trajectories. The latest wave was in 2022 at age 24. Data are available upon request.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Every other year', 2016, 2022, 'Limited to specific regions/areas', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 1400, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer without restrictions', 'https://www.jacobscenter.uzh.ch/en/research/zproso/aboutus.html', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, precise number', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, full ISCED for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('EE (Estonia)', 'Estonian Education Information System', 'EHIS', 'The Estonian Education Information System (EHIS) is a national register established in 2004 that compiles data across all school tracks. It includes information on students, teachers, institutions, curricula, diplomas, and educational support. Data are accessible upon registration and may be subject to fees.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2004, 'ongoing', 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Full access through request', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://www.ehis.ee/', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('EE (Estonia)', 'Eksamite Infosüsteemi (Examinations Information System)', 'EIS', 'The Examinations Information System (EIS) is Estonia’s national administrative system for collecting exam data from 9th and 12th grade students. It covers the years 2015 to 2024, with most exams missing in 2020. The system provides centralized data on student assessments. Access conditions are not publicly specified.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2015, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://eis.ekk.edu.ee/eis/eksamistatistika', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('LV (Latvia)', 'Centralised Exam Results', NULL, 'Latvia’s Centralised Exam Results system compiles national data on examination outcomes across all education levels and school types, from basic to higher education. It includes gymnasiums, vocational institutions, distance learning, and more. Anonymised aggregated data are available without restriction from the data provider’s website.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Pseudo-panel', 'Administrative', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2008, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Open data', 'On a personal computer without restrictions', 'https://stat.gov.lv/lv/statistikas-temas/izglitiba-kultura-zinatne/visparizglitojosas-skolas/cits/12464-centralizeto?themeCode=IA', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('LT (Lithuania)', 'NACIONALINIAI MOKINIŲ PASIEKIMŲ TYRIMAI (National Survey of Student Achievement )', 'NMPT (NSSA)', 'The National Survey of Student Achievement (NSSA) is a national assessment system in Lithuania, collecting data from 2nd, 4th, 6th, and 8th grade students. Conducted every other year, it includes only assessment data since 2012. Covering primary and middle secondary education, anonymised data are available without restrictions.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Hybrid', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Every other year', 2012, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Mixed (computer and paper-based)', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Open data', 'On a personal computer without restrictions', 'https://lida.dataverse.lt/dataverse/SurveyData_EST_NSSA', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes, only presence/absence', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the students)', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No'),
('PT (Portugal)', 'Sistema de Informação do Ministério da Educação e Ciência', 'MISI', 'The Sistema de Informação do Ministério da Educação e Ciência (MISI) is an administrative dataset in Portugal collecting grades and exam results at all levels from pre-school to secondary education. Established in 2006, it is updated at least annually. Microdata access is only possible on-site at the facilities of the data provider.', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Administrative', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No info', 'No info', 'No info', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2006, 'ongoing', 'National', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'On a computer belonging to the producer of the data, which is not connected to internet or to another computer (in this case the producer examines all the results outputs)', '"Not available"', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'Yes, specific country', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Administrative (provided by the institution or others)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No');
