('HU (Hungary)', 'KRTK’S Linked administrative panel dataset - Admin4', 'KRTK''S Admin4', 'Admin3 is a linked administrative panel dataset developed by KRTK in Hungary, similar to Admin4. It covers all pupils and tracks educational and labour market trajectories using data from multiple administrative sources. The dataset allows longitudinal analysis from 2003 to 2017. Microdata access is restricted and subject to formal request and approval.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Repeated cross-section', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2007, 2021, 'National', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'N/A', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'On a personal computer with a specific interface', 'https://adatbank.krtk.mta.hu/en/adatbazisok/elerheto-adatbazisok/', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified information for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, simplified ISCED for both parents', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Not clear'),
('NL (Netherlands)', 'PRIMary to Secondary education (PRIMS), Cohort 1', 'PRIMS (C1)', 'PRIMS  Cohort 1 is a 1.5-year longitudinal study conducted in the Netherlands from 2020 to 2021. It focuses on the role of peer relationships during the transition from primary to secondary education, aiming to understand how these relationships influence educational inequalities and students'' social integration. Data collection involved surveys administered to students in their final year of primary school and again after transitioning to secondary school. The dataset includes information on peer networks, educational aspirations, and academic performance. Access to the data is restricted and will be made available to researchers under certain conditions in 2024.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Survey', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2020, 2020, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 2000, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'Not clear', 'https://www.nationaalcohortonderzoek.nl/prims', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by the student)', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, only presence/absence', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear'),
('NL (Netherlands)', 'PRIMary to Secondary education (PRIMS), Cohort 2', 'PRIMS (C2)', 'PRIMS Cohort 2 is a 2 year longitudinal study conducted in the Netherlands, focusing on the role of peer relationships during the transition from primary to secondary education. Data collection involved surveys administered to students in their final year of primary school and again after transitioning to secondary school. The dataset includes information on peer networks, educational aspirations, and academic performance. Access to the data is restricted and will be made available to researchers under certain conditions in 2024.', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Pure longitudinal', 'Hybrid', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yearly (or more than once per year)', 2021, 2022, 'National', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Not clear', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Yes', 1200, 'No', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No Access or Limited Access Under Specific Conditions', 'Not clear', 'https://www.nationaalcohortonderzoek.nl/prims', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes, only presence/absence', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes, detailed information (e.g. ISCO code) for both parents', 'Yes, for both parents', 'No', 'Yes, for both parents', 'Yes', 'Yes, specific country', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'Both self-reported and administrative', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'No', 'No', 'Self-reported (provided by teachers)', 'Linkable to the ones of students', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'Not clear');
